subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Liezel Huber and Lisa Raymond defeated the defending champions, Vania King and Yaroslava Shvedova, 4-6, 7-6 (5), 7-6 (3), and claimed the No. 1 world ranking.
